	<h4>Directions</h4>
	<p>By default, dropdowns will dropdown below the trigger element. By utilizing the <code>data-direction</code> attribute, we can change the direction of the dropdow to <code>left</code>, <code>right</code> or <code>up</code>.</p>
	<div class="markup-panel">
		<div class="markup-panel__example">
<div class="ter-dropdown" data-direction="left">
	<button role="button" class="ter-dropdown__toggle ter-button ter-button--dark">Drop Left</button>
	<ul class="ter-dropdown__menu">
		<li class="ter-dropdown__item ter-dropdown__item--no-link">My Account</li>
